---
title: Veggie Fritter & Haloumi Stack with Roasted Kumara Toss & Sweet Chilli Sauce
description: These juicy sweet-and-salty fritters are the perfect marriage of flavours and easy cooking techniques. Each fritter is packed with
veggies, and is stacked with tasty haloumi and sweet chilli sauce to add plenty of cheesy goodness!

